was going to come back.

5
00:00:12,910 --> 00:00:14,980
Hey, do you know
what day it is today?

6
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:16,310
Is it your birthday?

7
00:00:16,310 --> 00:00:17,250
Nope.

8
00:00:17,250 --> 00:00:18,750
Is it Miss Asahina's birthday?

9
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:19,910
Wrong!

10
00:00:19,910 --> 00:00:21,620
It is Koizumi
or Nagato's birthday?

11
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:22,980
