those are!

12
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:24,420
By the way, my birthday is...

13
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:26,010
That doesn't matter.

14
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:30,830
You don't know what an important
day it is today, do you?

15
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:34,190
It's just a hot weekday
to me.

16
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:37,030
