the month it is.

17
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,020
July seventh...

18
00:00:39,930 --> 00:00:43,870
Are you saying that you've been
talking about Tanabata?

19
00:00:43,870 --> 00:00:46,840
Of course I'm talking about Tanabata!
It's Tanabata today!

20
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:50,210
You're Japanese, you've got to
remember these kinds of things!

21
00:00:50,210 --> 00:00:51,550
I see.

22
00:00:51,550 --> 00:00:54,680
I always make sure to take part
in events like these.

23
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:58,620
This year, the whole SOS Brigade
is going to make this a huge affair!

24
00:00:58,620 --> 00:00:59,880
And here we go.

25
