when Haruhi gets going
about something.

29
00:01:18,670 --> 00:01:22,070
I kind of hate the fact
that I'm getting used to it.

30
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:24,980
Yes?

31
00:01:24,980 --> 00:01:26,210
Hey.

32
00:01:26,210 --> 00:01:27,220
Hello.

33
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:29,520
Hello.
How are you doing?

34
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:32,980
Things have been crazy for me
ever since I started high school.

35
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:34,720
Here you go.

36
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,090
Thank you.

37
00:01:36,090 --> 00:01:37,560
You're welcome.

38
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,320
Would you like to
try this out?

39
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:42,030
We'll eventually get bored
of othello, after all.

40
00:01:42,030 --> 00:01:44,300
Unfortunately, I don't know
the rules.

41
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,800
That's too bad.

42
