come true during Tanabata?

55
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,470
Orihime and Hikoboshi, right?

56
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:23,870
Well, that's correct.
Ten points.

57
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:26,770
