So if you wish for a boyfriend
by this Christmas or something,

78
00:03:05,550 --> 00:03:06,950
it won't get there
in time!

79
00:03:06,950 --> 00:03:08,720
If it takes that long
to go one way,

80
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:12,190
