for it to make the round trip?

81
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:15,420
Well, they're gods, so they'll
think of something.

82
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:16,890
It's like a half-price
summer bargain.

83
00:03:16,890 --> 00:03:19,490
What happened to "according to
the theory of relativity"?

84
00:03:19,490 --> 00:03:22,400
Here are two tanzaku, one each
for Vega and Altair.

85
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:27,070
So, write wishes that you want to
come true in 25 and 16 years!

86
00:03:27,070 --> 00:03:31,370
