lock the door, okay?

128
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,940
In that case,
I'll be going, too.

129
00:05:47,410 --> 00:05:48,430
Lucky me!

130
00:05:51,450 --> 00:05:52,340
Hey...

131
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,240
