132
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:56,810
Right.

133
00:05:58,150 --> 00:06:01,190
Thank goodness we were able
to stay behind so naturally.

134
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:04,280
Is this something that it would be bad
for the others to hear?

135
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,890
Yes...

136
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:11,100
There's a particular place that
I want you to come with me to.

137
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:13,330
That's fine.
Where are we going?

138
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,470
Umm...

139
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,010
Three years... ago...

140
00:06:19,010 --> 00:06:20,170
Thr...

141
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:23,170
I'm sorry to be making
such a strange request!

142
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:27,050
You can't?

143
00:06:27,050 --> 00:06:29,250
So this would be
time travel, then?

144
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:30,820
Yes, that's right.

145
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:33,180
