152
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,780
She's cute!

153
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:55,470
Well...

154
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:57,680
Okay, I'll go.

155
00:06:57,680 --> 00:07:00,620
Really? Thank you!

156
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:01,880
So cute!

157
00:07:02,450 --> 00:07:05,720
Oh, thank goodness...

158
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,190
Now that I think about it,

159
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:09,720
the only time that Miss Asahina's
mentioned she's from the future

160
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,560
is when she admitted it
to me,

161
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:15,330
and the only proof of it is the existence
of the adult Miss Asahina.

162
00:07:15,330 --> 00:07:18,300
This is a perfect chance for me
to confirm

163
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:20,440
that she's a girl
from the future.

164
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,900
So, where's your
time machine?

165
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,110
We'll be leaving
from here.

166
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,200
From here?

167
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:35,310
Kyon... I'm sorry.

168
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,220
Oh, you're awake!

169
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:47,760
Please wake up soon...

170
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,920
My legs have
gone numb.

171
00:07:56,540 --> 00:07:58,710
Why was I asleep?

172
00:07:58,710 --> 00:08:03,270
I'm sorry, but I didn't want you to
see how time jumping is performed.

173
00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:05,610
Because it's classified information...

174
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:08,480
Umm... are you mad?

175
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,880
No, not at all.

176
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:12,090
If it was Haruhi that did it,
I'd hit her.

177
00:08:12,090 --> 00:08:14,360
But since it's you,
it's completely okay.

178
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,620
Thank goodness.

179
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:18,390
So it's three years ago?

180
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:20,930
July seventh,
three years ago.

181
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:22,600
I'd guess around
nine PM?

182
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,630
Really?

183
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:24,790
Really.

184
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:32,300
This is the same park that Nagato
invited me to some time ago.

185
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:35,270
Is this a Mecca
for unusual people?

186
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,640
Miss Asahina?

187
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:44,540
Um...

188
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:51,060
Could this be some sort of
declaration of intent?

189
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,900
Hello, Kyon.

190
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,270
Miss Asahina!

191
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,000
So this is how I looked
back then.

192
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:14,520
It was her role
to guide you here.

193
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:17,450
Guiding you from this point on
is mine.

194
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:20,220
Are you the one that put
Miss Asahina to sleep?

195
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:23,930
I couldn't let her
see me,

196
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:28,000
because when I was here, as her,
I didn't meet me.

197
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,330
Right...

198
