the sleeping me there a kiss.

207
00:09:59,130 --> 00:10:00,860
But only while she's asleep.

208
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:03,630
That's a little...

209
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,830
On an emotional
and on a situational level,

210
00:10:05,830 --> 00:10:07,570
doing that would go against
my principles.

211
00:10:07,570 --> 00:10:08,930
But, well, even still...

212
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,210
It's time.
I have to go.

213
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:15,410
Also, you have to keep my being here
a secret from her.

214
00:10:15,410 --> 00:10:16,670
Promise me.

215
00:10:17,410 --> 00:10:18,840
Will you pinky swear
with me?

216
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,010
Okay, you've sworn!

217
00:10:24,350 --> 00:10:25,990
Good bye, Kyon.

218
00:10:25,990 --> 00:10:27,220
See you later.

219
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:33,460
I wonder how long
it's been

220
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:36,300
