224
00:10:45,810 --> 00:10:48,140
Maybe I should call 411.

225
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:51,170
East Junior High, huh?

226
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,510
Hey.

227
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,290
Who are you?

228
00:11:03,290 --> 00:11:06,290
It does certainly seem like
I've gone back three years.

229
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:09,530
This is Haruhi Suzumiya,
currently a seventh grader.

230
00:11:09,530 --> 00:11:11,800
I asked you
who you were.

231
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:13,800
