with this?

248
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,280
Draw lines the way
I tell you to.

249
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,150
Me?

250
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:05,520
Right, you.

251
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:08,420
Because I'm the director.

252
